Initialize InMobi  Initialize the plugin where appropriate in your code. We recommend to do this in the  AppDelegate::applicationDidFinishLaunching()  or  AppController:didFinishLaunchingWithOptions() . Make sure to include the appropriate headers:  #include  PluginInMobi/PluginInMobi.h 
